# Sentinx console (Next.js) — local env template. Copy to `.env.local` and adjust.
#
# Base URL the BFF proxy (app/api/[...path]/route.ts) forwards browser /api/* calls to.
# This is the FastAPI backend at the repo root (`uvicorn app:app --port 8080`).
BACKEND_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:8080

# Notes:
# - The browser never holds the JWT: login stores it in an httpOnly `sx_jwt` cookie, and the
#   [...path] proxy re-attaches it as `Authorization: Bearer <jwt>` server-side.
# - Pages /new and /runs/* require that cookie — sign in at /login first.
# - Full both-halves bring-up + smoke test: ../design documentation/RUNBOOK.md
